<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV24">
<l>iyalvā yiṉavañca nōykoṇ ṭulāvu mōrōkuṭaṅkaik</l>
<l>kayalpāy vaṉaperu nīrkkaṇkaḷ tammoṭuṅ kuṉṟamoṉṟāṟ</l>
<l>puyalvā yiṉanirai kāttapuḷ ḷūrtikaḷ ḷūruntuḻāyk</l>
<l>koyalvāy malarmēl maṉattoṭeṉ ṉāṅkoleṅ kōlvaḷaikkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With [our] big wet eyes as for one thing, [like] carps leaping in [our] palms,</l>
<l>that roam about with cruel pain which has become natural, and with [our] mind</l>
<l>on the nectar-leaking Tulsi blossoms with choice mouths of [him with] the bird vehicle</l>
<l>who guarded the cow herd in the rain by means of just one hill, what will become of our bangles in a row?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
